<br>
*) Change Ragefire to be a level 30 drake mob that is easily within killable range by people in the zone.<br>
<br>
*) Change the quest drop to be highly desireable by all newbies everywhere, but make it a rare drop. It should preferably be NO DROP, but not LORE because the druids should have the chance to stock up on extras so they can sell MQ rights and get better equipment and spells.<br>
<br>
*) The final turn-in mob should spawn only when the Sister of the Spire has been killed. During the 3 days it takes your guild to work its way through PoA you can powerlevel the druid to the point where he can go turn in the quest drop for you.<br>
<br>
*) And since this is now much easier than camping Ragefire in Skyfire, the Overking and Ixilblat drops should be changed from always-drop to a 5-10% chance of dropping (and the Overking and Ixilblat changed to rare spawns with 20 wandering placeholders) and the Plasmatic Robe should be changed from always-drop in Temple of Sol Ro to an infrequent drop off High Priest M'Kari.<br>
<br>
Those few little changes would bring the insanely hard cleric epic quest in line with the ridiculously easy magician epic.<br>
<br>
----------<br>
<br>
And before I gather more flames than Solusek himself, let me point out that I have helped camp and kill Ragefire on more than one occasion. Yes, it is frustrating, and moreso because it is the last step in the cleric epic quest, but it is in no way, shape, or form comparable to some other epic bottlenecks out there. At the absolute least, you and a few friends can rack up some serious experience and stock up on Kunark spells while you wait. If you are vigilent and determined, you can beat any guild that isn't already in Skyfire when Rage decides to spawn. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page  <b>1</b> <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerrants.showMessageRange?topicID=260.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerrants.showMessageRange?topicID=260.topic&start=41&stop=56>3</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerrants.showPrevMessage?topicID=260.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerrants.showNextMessage?topicID=260.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerrants.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=260.topic&index=20><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerrants.threadControl?topicID=260.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/unread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerrants.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=260.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerrants.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=260.topic>Unsub